\ls1\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Montauk 3.0 is a fully automated pipeline that generates (or accepts ideas from human user) strategies, backtests the strategies, then runs the backtested strategies through to validation suite (to guarantee no overfitting or any other issues) then adds the resulting, verified, validated strategies to the leaderboard. It is a full pipeline that strings together strategy ideation, backtesting, validation and overfit testing, and leaderboard addition. \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
